{
  "stem": "20800.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the from the tank-- an officer or what, I don't remember-- but he jumped out and rushed to me and took his hat and put on mine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I, I had it even now, this hat, because it's very-- I was happy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were crying, and they start to-- don't cry, don't cry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We come, you free, all sort of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the happiest day of my life and the day that I was waiting for three years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and of course, they straight away wanted to help us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The tanks went, and then after them come officers in, in cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of the captain officer come and said to us, stop crying, sit-- go to the car.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We take you to the house, and you take whatever you wanted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dress yourself, take this thing off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You look horrible [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And really, they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us in the car, and they start to go and, and ask which villa you want?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we say, for us, it was no different.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wherever we go, we wanted to wash.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We want to be able to sit down properly in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they took us to one villa-- it was two-story house-- and, and said, you can stay here, whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever it is here, it's all yours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, [INAUDIBLE] I was all the time I was in concentration camp, my dream was when they free me, the first thing I wanted is a big piece of bread, and that's what will be the top of my dreams come true.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they free me, and they said, we have in this villa-- downstairs it was a cellar.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All sort of things there were.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
